 Madrina Veteran Nigerian dancehall and hip hop artiste, Madrina (Cynthia Morgan) has said Davido has ignored her after he promised to help her. Recall Madrina revealed some secrets about her former management which caught the attention of Davido and made a promise to help the singer. Speaking about the aftermath of the promise, she said nothing has happened, there hasn’t been any meeting. According to her, she has made several calls to Davido and none has been returned. She acknowledged having been sent a record by OBO himself to add her verse. but even that, she is done with it but hasn’t heard anything from him in the last 3 months.